			<phrase strongs="3478">all Israel,</phrase>
			<phrase strongs="5674">and passed over</phrase>
			<phrase strongs="3383">Jordan,</phrase>
			<phrase strongs="935">and came</phrase>
			<phrase strongs="6186">upon them, and set the battle in array</phrase>
